Title: Back to Headquarters! Again!
Description:
You've done truly incredible work! The proof is obvious: you are, in fact, a proper Azerothian Archivist.

Meet us all back at our headquarters in Thaldraszus. Eadweard would like codify all your helpful labors and achievements for our group.
ObjectivesText: Meet with Eadweard Dalyngrigge at the Algeth'ar Academy in Thaldraszus.
